WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:02.636
Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.670 --> 00:04.405
I blackmailed them.

00:04.438 --> 00:06.274
All of them.
The donors.

00:06.307 --> 00:09.610
- What do you want?
- I've done enough.

00:09.643 --> 00:11.479
- They blackmailed you too,
didn't they?

00:11.512 --> 00:16.250
Your mom, she passed.
They said she went peacefully.

00:16.283 --> 00:18.286
- I married your sister, Sarah.

00:18.319 --> 00:21.689
Don't you wanna just scream
in your family's face,

00:21.722 --> 00:23.524
"I exist"?

00:23.557 --> 00:25.369
- Of course I do, but you can't
change other people.

00:25.393 --> 00:27.095
- I'm doing 8R.

00:27.128 --> 00:29.430
I'm climbing the rungs
with Richard and Felicia.

00:29.463 --> 00:31.665
- Hi.
- Ashley, hi.

00:31.699 --> 00:36.137
- How's Hawk?
- He's living in the city.

00:36.170 --> 00:39.473
- Everything I said up there
was about you.

00:42.510 --> 00:46.314
*

00:50.651 --> 00:57.591
*

