You know,
you kinda look like him now.

23:57.003 --> 23:58.237
Is that part of it?

23:58.270 --> 23:59.839
Was it your initiation
or something?

23:59.872 --> 24:02.208
- No.

24:02.241 --> 24:06.212
I just... I was ready
