26:49.275 --> 26:50.342
- What?

26:50.376 --> 26:53.713
- You seem... weird.

26:53.746 --> 26:55.047
Doesn't she seem weird, Dad?

26:55.081 --> 26:56.282
- Are you weird, babe?

26:56.315 --> 26:58.951
- No.
- Just hungry.

