27:07.093 --> 27:08.333
Joy, do you mind grabbing that?

27:08.360 --> 27:09.996
- Hello?

27:11.864 --> 27:12.965
I...

27:15.334 --> 27:17.069
Who is it?

27:18.437 --> 27:20.707
- Hello, Sarah.
- What are you doing here, Tess?

27:20.740 --> 27:22.408
- Restitution, right, Dad?

27:22.441 --> 27:26.212
Thought I'd stop by and remind
you all that I still exist.

27:28.180 --> 27:31.017
Well, isn't anyone
gonna say hello?

27:31.050 --> 27:32.885
* *

27:32.919 --> 27:33.986
- Hello, Tessa.

27:34.020 --> 27:35.788
- Hello, Cal.

27:35.822 --> 27:36.823
- Who is she?

27:36.856 --> 27:38.157
- Tessa.

27:38.190 --> 27:40.960
- Wow, Russel.
- You know my name.

27:40.993 --> 27:42.361
You got old.

27:42.394 --> 27:44.831
- It's really not a good time,
Tessa.

27:44.864 --> 27:47.299
Why don't we do this
when the kids aren't around?

27:47.333 --> 27:49.702
- Your ex said
you'd have my back.

27:49.736 --> 27:51.103
- Eddie?

27:51.137 --> 27:53.773
- Yeah, we were having coffee
the other day.

27:53.806 --> 27:55.775
Why did you get
in touch with Eddie?

27:55.808 --> 27:57.043
He got in touch with me.

27:57.076 --> 27:58.277
- You know my dad?

27:58.310 --> 27:59.879
Hey, come on upstairs, Summer.

27:59.912 --> 28:02.281
Let's... let's all go upstairs.
Come one.

28:02.314 --> 28:04.483
*

28:04.516 --> 28:06.753
- What did Eddie want with you?

28:06.786 --> 28:08.755
- I don't know.
- Guess he's sad and mad

28:08.788 --> 28:09.965
'cause he's not used to
how fucked up

28:09.989 --> 28:11.257
this whole situation is.

28:11.290 --> 28:12.959
- Why don't we step outside,
Tessa?

28:12.992 --> 28:15.127
- I'm sorry, Cal.
- Are you part of this family now?

28:15.161 --> 28:16.504
Because I'm trying
to talk to my family.

28:16.528 --> 28:18.230
- Hello, Mom.
- Hey, let me walk you...

28:18.264 --> 28:19.975
- Leave me alone.
- You're worse than all of them.

28:19.999 --> 28:21.500
Mom, please, look at me.

28:21.533 --> 28:23.069
Look at me, Mom.
Look at me.

28:23.102 --> 28:25.304
- I need you to go.
- Now.

28:26.505 --> 28:28.040
Please.

28:28.074 --> 28:29.742
We can talk later privately.

28:29.776 --> 28:31.844
And I would like that very much,
to talk to you,

28:31.878 --> 28:33.379
but this is not the way
to do it.

28:33.412 --> 28:35.281
- Do they know
you were gonna come with me?

28:35.314 --> 28:38.217
Did they? Did you guys all know
your great Guardian of the Light

28:38.250 --> 28:41.387
had her fucking bags packed?
Did you?

28:41.420 --> 28:44.991
I waited for you in
Grand Central for three hours,

28:45.024 --> 28:46.358
but you didn't come.

28:46.392 --> 28:48.194
- I was a kid.

28:48.227 --> 28:51.230
- Do you know the things
I had to do to get by?

28:51.263 --> 28:52.865
- Look at me, do you?
- I was a kid.

28:52.899 --> 28:55.334
- But I did them.
- I did them, and I got out.

28:55.367 --> 28:57.003
And I have a great life now.

28:57.036 --> 28:58.437
I have a great life.

28:58.470 --> 29:00.907
Do you hear me?
I have a great life.

29:00.940 --> 29:02.809
*

29:02.842 --> 29:07.113
Your ex said if we forced you
to see us, you would.

29:07.146 --> 29:11.117
He was wrong.
He was wrong.

29:11.150 --> 29:18.090
*

29:26.098 --> 29:33.039
*

