I wonder what
my parents would do

29:43.449 --> 29:46.118
if I walked into their house.

29:56.562 --> 29:58.330
- You okay, Mom?

30:01.100 --> 30:02.268
- Gab...
- No.

30:05.938 --> 30:07.039
How long?

30:07.073 --> 30:09.308
- How long what?

30:09.341 --> 30:11.010
- 15 years.

30:15.181 --> 30:16.382
- I...

30:19.418 --> 30:21.187
I need to be alone.

30:21.220 --> 30:23.856
- What? What's going on?
- What's 15 years?

30:26.525 --> 30:28.260
Dad, what's 15 years?

30:28.294 --> 30:29.929
- God, Russel.

30:29.962 --> 30:32.899
He's been seeing your sister
for 15 years.

30:35.001 --> 30:36.502
- She's my daughter.

30:36.535 --> 30:38.905
- Let's get the kids.
- Go home.

30:38.938 --> 30:42.374
- You'd do the same
if one of yours took off.

30:42.408 --> 30:44.911
- Maybe.

30:44.944 --> 30:46.879
But I wouldn't lie about it.

30:50.282 --> 30:52.151
Come on, let's go!

30:52.184 --> 30:53.285
I don't wanna go!

30:53.319 --> 30:54.453
Well, too bad.

30:54.486 --> 30:56.088
Get in the car!

30:59.125 --> 31:01.527
*

31:01.560 --> 31:03.529
- I love you.

31:03.562 --> 31:09.435
*

31:09.468 --> 31:12.438
- You had your bags packed?

31:12.471 --> 31:14.573
- I was a kid.

31:14.606 --> 31:18.310
And I wanted to be free.

31:18.344 --> 31:20.646
We would stay up all night

31:20.679 --> 31:24.383
planning our escape.

31:24.416 --> 31:27.519
But I couldn't do it.

31:27.553 --> 31:30.389
And then as I got older,

31:30.422 --> 31:33.225
I was grateful I stayed.

31:33.259 --> 31:36.428
I started to believe
that The Light saved me

31:36.462 --> 31:39.431
from walking out of my life.

31:39.465 --> 31:43.335
I just don't understand
why Eddie would do this.

31:43.369 --> 31:45.204
- He's angry.

31:45.237 --> 31:48.074
He's acting viciously.

31:48.107 --> 31:51.210
He was probably hoping
Hawk would be here

31:51.243 --> 31:53.412
and Hawk would find out
that you tried to leave

31:53.445 --> 31:55.414
the same age that he was
when he tried to leave.

31:55.447 --> 31:57.049
- You know, I deserve

31:57.083 --> 31:58.517
what just happened in there.

31:58.550 --> 32:00.086
- No...
- No, I deserve it.

32:00.119 --> 32:02.088
- No, no, you don't, Sarah.

32:02.121 --> 32:05.724
- Marshall Small died.

32:05.757 --> 32:08.060
- From Clarksville?

32:08.094 --> 32:09.261
I'm so sorry to hear that.

32:09.295 --> 32:11.430
- And there's nothing.

32:11.463 --> 32:16.035
There's no action that
I can take to make things right.

32:16.068 --> 32:17.336
- Mm.

32:19.505 --> 32:22.674
You will find a way

32:22.708 --> 32:25.544
to do something for Marshal,
you will.

32:25.577 --> 32:31.117
But as long as you hold on
to guilt about Eddie,

32:31.150 --> 32:34.286
you'll never be free
to live the life,

32:34.320 --> 32:38.457
to have the love
that you deserve.

32:45.464 --> 32:48.200
- I need to put Summer to bed.

32:55.074 --> 32:57.509
- Relinquish it tomorrow, Sarah.

32:59.578 --> 33:02.114
I-I don't want to be your sin.

33:05.417 --> 33:08.587
* Last night I tried
to find my demon *

33:08.620 --> 33:12.458
* He was gone

33:12.491 --> 33:16.295
* My hand stretched out
to hold him *

33:16.328 --> 33:20.699
* And he slipped
right through my fingers *

33:20.732 --> 33:24.503
* Never in my life

33:24.536 --> 33:26.438
*

33:26.472 --> 33:30.442
- I've been living a double life
for too long.

33:30.476 --> 33:33.212
It's exhausting.

33:33.245 --> 33:36.215
You start to lose sight
of everything.

33:36.248 --> 33:38.117
Who you are, what you want.

33:38.150 --> 33:39.394
And now that
they're blackmailing me,

33:39.418 --> 33:41.487
making it worse,

33:41.520 --> 33:43.589
I think this is the moment

33:43.622 --> 33:45.291
that you blow it up,
and come clean.

33:45.324 --> 33:47.493
- We'd lose everything.
- Everyone.

33:47.526 --> 33:49.228
- Not necessarily.

33:49.261 --> 33:52.564
You know, maybe we can
get the Feds to cut us a deal,

33:52.598 --> 33:54.566
help us keep it quiet.

33:54.600 --> 33:56.735
- I don't know.

33:56.768 --> 34:02.641
*

34:02.674 --> 34:05.444
- Well, you have to decide
for yourself.

34:05.477 --> 34:07.346
But me,

34:07.379 --> 34:11.117
I'm not about to start letting
these people control me,

34:11.150 --> 34:13.351
judge me,
tell me how to live my life.

34:13.385 --> 34:15.286
I'm putting a stop
to these motherfuckers

34:15.321 --> 34:19.558
who promised me I could unburden
without any repercussions.

34:19.591 --> 34:22.261
*

34:25.297 --> 34:29.735
*

34:37.243 --> 34:38.610
- Hey, you know the woman

34:38.643 --> 34:40.411
who gave you
"The Wizard of Oz" book?

34:40.446 --> 34:44.350
She wasn't a friend
of my mom's from college.

34:44.382 --> 34:46.717
- Who was she?

34:46.752 --> 34:49.388
- She's a counselor.

34:49.420 --> 34:54.760
My parents, they hired her
to get me back home.

34:57.896 --> 34:59.531
- And you knew who she was

34:59.565 --> 35:02.501
when you asked me
to go to the baby shower?

35:04.236 --> 35:06.872
You lied to me.

35:06.905 --> 35:08.874
Why?

35:08.907 --> 35:11.710
- Because I'm thinking
of going home.

35:11.743 --> 35:14.346
And I want you to come with me.

35:14.380 --> 35:17.216
Look, just talk to Wendy
one more time, okay?

35:17.249 --> 35:19.185
She can help you see.

35:19.218 --> 35:22.854
We can have a life
somewhere else,

35:22.888 --> 35:24.890
a life we make together.

35:24.923 --> 35:29.261
- And if I don't wanna go,
will you go without me?

35:29.295 --> 35:33.432
- The only thing
that's keeping me here is you.

35:33.465 --> 35:40.406
*

35:46.912 --> 35:51.550
You asked
why I broke up with you?

35:51.583 --> 35:54.720
- I know things were difficult
with your family

35:54.753 --> 35:56.722
and everything.

36:00.992 --> 36:03.595
- Yeah,
but it was more than that.

36:08.567 --> 36:12.238
Cal offered us a house
if I broke up with you.

36:15.474 --> 36:16.442
- What?

36:16.475 --> 36:17.943
- My family needed it.

36:17.976 --> 36:19.211
And I...

36:19.245 --> 36:22.248
I couldn't...

36:22.281 --> 36:24.483
I wish I had the strength
to say no to him, but...

36:24.516 --> 36:25.627
- That doesn't make any sense.

36:25.651 --> 36:27.286
Why would Cal do that?

36:27.319 --> 36:28.854
- Because he didn't want
to lose you.

36:28.887 --> 36:31.523
He and your mom.

36:31.557 --> 36:33.792
He's not the amazing man
that you think he is.

36:33.825 --> 36:35.665
You dad, he would have
never that to you, Hawk.

36:35.694 --> 36:39.498
- You don't know a fucking thing
about my dad

36:39.531 --> 36:42.301
or Cal or any of it.

36:42.334 --> 36:44.236
- I have hated myself
for what I did to you.

36:44.270 --> 36:46.672
- And I'm telling you now...
- You should have told me then.

36:46.705 --> 36:48.807
- Yeah, I know, and I'm sorry.

36:51.577 --> 36:53.545
- This is... this is...
- Look, I really, really

36:53.579 --> 36:54.889
wanted to tell you,
but I didn't know how.

36:54.913 --> 36:56.382
- Great.

37:02.854 --> 37:05.691
Hawk.

37:05.724 --> 37:07.893
Hawk!

37:07.926 --> 37:14.866
*

37:17.703 --> 37:21.373
* Stranded by this

37:21.407 --> 37:24.610
* Open window

37:24.643 --> 37:25.777
* All my debts unfold

37:28.880 --> 37:30.516
- Sarah.
- Why?

37:30.549 --> 37:33.419
Are you trying to hurt me?
My family?

37:33.452 --> 37:34.653
- Sarah.
- Tessa.

37:34.686 --> 37:36.855
She comes over to the house.

37:36.888 --> 37:38.657
Summer is there,
and she's shouting at me.

37:38.690 --> 37:40.626
She's shouting at my mother.

37:40.659 --> 37:42.003
- I didn't know
she was gonna do that.

37:42.027 --> 37:43.462
- Why are you even
talking to her?

37:43.495 --> 37:45.297
- Look, I can talk to people,
Sarah.

37:45.331 --> 37:47.466
I can reach out.
This is my experience too.

37:47.499 --> 37:49.000
I'm just trying
to figure things out.

37:49.034 --> 37:50.802
- No, no.
- But you made it about us.

37:50.836 --> 37:54.840
You made it about hurting
my mother, my dad, my brother.

37:54.873 --> 37:57.976
- That, I apologize...
- No, and you hurt me.

37:58.009 --> 38:01.313
Will you let me go, please?

38:01.347 --> 38:03.415
You have to let me go.

38:03.449 --> 38:05.584
- I can't do that.
- You have to.

38:05.617 --> 38:07.353
*

38:07.386 --> 38:10.021
* As I let them go

38:10.055 --> 38:11.022
* Water cries from my soul

38:11.056 --> 38:12.391
